{"tid":2138093,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"（真係發夢）香港有個秘密監獄","createTime":"2020-08-03T11:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T15:18:03.000Z","uid":277187,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46d8cc3f0398bd21fd7af2ad4a506156809d90c5","tid":2138093,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ha2ScEO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fha2ScEO.jpg&h=7e791cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我尋晚發咗個好恐怖嘅夢<br />\n發夢喺香港某啲區域設立咗檢查關卡，<br />\n有國安駐守，過關要出示證件，<br />\n好多人都避免去呢啲有關卡嘅地方，<br />\n因為唔想檢查期間有咩令國安起疑會被拉。<br />\n我唔知點解想經過關卡睇下裡面係點運作，<br />\n諗住自己身家清白就入去。<br />\n入去首先有人check我證件<br />\n（明明香港境內要check證件）<br />\n然後個女人睇咗好耐，<br />\n我諗住要搜我袋，<br />\n點知佢叫我要照x光，<br />\n睇下有冇肺花先可以過關。<br />\n咁我就入左去照，<br />\n照完去咗個地方等，<br />\n個度都有其他人，<br />\n我唔知點解一個人行開咗去一個地方，<br />\n個度不見天日，係五六層樓嘅監獄咁，<br />\n每層有鐵籠同大電視，<br />\n大電視影住呢度被困嘅人，<br />\n每個籠都迫滿人，<br />\n好多人喺度叫，<br />\n電視度會影住啲人大頭，<br />\n睇到基本上知名嘅抗爭者都喺晒度，<br />\n而出面嘅人係知道佢地被國安拉晒，<br />\n但唔知佢地就困喺度。<br />\n望住呢個監獄畫面嚇到醒咗....."},{"pid":"d57c1a5f3ff8e6c99a1754ab29bf92b9a00b0052","tid":2138093,"uid":311663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e050317f3afd331315ed75230f64973eb746a31","tid":2138093,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d57c1a5f3ff8e6c99a1754ab29bf92b9a00b0052","tid":2138093,"uid":311663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T11:39:59.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76dc2ced4bee155be39c7bc103d499c14e4f196a","tid":2138093,"uid":55658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b7ba2107100088798e3b5fd1a666961ffa7f901","tid":2138093,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:17:15.000Z","msg":"唔係故仔，純粹share下夢境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d7a22440dfcf2b6ae41d48857059f0c3f7b420","tid":2138093,"uid":277187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲都有發埋啲咁嘅夢？"}]}